nnn
Tags: file-managers, minimal

Minimal terminal file manager focused on speed and low overhead.

Important note:
The help calls it "The unorthodox terminal file manager."

Help head:
usage: nnn [OPTIONS] [PATH]
PATH   start dir/file [default: .]
-d     detail mode
-e     text in $VISUAL/$EDITOR/vi
-H     show hidden files
-o     open files only on Enter
-z     in order fuzzy filters

> nnn -h
